Rhian Brewster has been left out of Liverpool&rsquo;s matchday squad for the Carabao Cup trip to Lincoln City as he moves closer to resolving his future, with Sheffield United still heading the queue to sign him. #awlfc [<br />
@MelissaReddy_]<br />
<br />
Sheffield United manager Chris Wilder and Liverpool&rsquo;s Jurgen Klopp had another discussion about the young forward on Wednesday. Brewster has been Wilder&rsquo;s first choice to add to his offensive options. #awlfc [<br />
@MelissaReddy_]<br />
<br />
Sheffield United have received glowing reports on the player&rsquo;s attitude, application and ambition and are hoping to reach an agreement with Liverpool before one of their league rivals formally submit a proposal. #awlfc [<br />
@MelissaReddy_]

